dc:description: A large comb made from three pieces of wood with pegs in between. Five concentric circle designs are along the bottom of the front of the comb. The handle has a thumb groove and triangle design at the bottom of the handle. The back side has three beveled and a wear mark in the center. The end of the handle is also beveled. No traces of paint.
